# Newer release require springframework >= 4.0.7.RELEASE
Version:       1.5.2
Release:       alt1_8jpp8
Summary:       MongoDB support for Spring Data
License:       ASL 2.0
URL:           http://projects.spring.io/spring-data-mongodb/
